== PCS Project Installer ==

Scripts to install PCS projects, create task controller and job manager
directories, and default configuration files.



= Code and Directory Relationships =

Installing a specific project is performed by calling inst/inst_proj.

inst_proj calls scripts from supp/ to perform specific installation actions.



= Directory and File Description =
inst/          Installation scripts.
  inst_proj    Called by user to install project.

supp/          Supporting scripts for installation scripts.
  crp          Create project directory structure and configuration file.
  crt          Create task directory structure and configuration file.
  dproj        Download project-specific code from source repository.



= Usage Summary =

See the header of inst/inst_proj for a specific usage example.